com.bigdata.rdf.sparql.ast

Interface IReorderableNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BOp, Cloneable, IBindingProducerNode, IGroupMemberNode, IPropertySet, IQueryNode, IVariableBindingRequirements, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ArbitraryLengthPathNode, PropertyPathUnionNode, StatementPatternNode, UnionNode

    public interface IReorderableNode
extends IGroupMemberNode, IBindingProducerNode, BOp
    Interface for things which can be re-ordered by the static join optimizer. Currently limited to StatementPatternNodes and some instances of ArbitraryLengthPathNodes (those with a single statement pattern inside).
